<div class="s2"> [<a href="/vx.php?id=zb02">Previous</a>] [<a href="/vx.php?id=zidx">Index</a>] [<a href="/vx.php?id=zc00">Next</a>] <h1> C.R.I.S</h1>Computer Research & Information Service<br clear="all"/><script type="text/rocketscript">var disqus_url = 'http://vxheaven.org/vx.php?id=zc10';</script><a href="/vx.php?id=zc10#disqus_thread">Comments</a><br/><div style="float:left;"><div style="float: left;"><strong>Download</strong></div><div style="float: left;"> (<a href="/vx.php?id=zc10&amp;mode=full">Full info</a>)</div><br clear="all"/><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1"><tr bgcolor="#aaa999"><th>&nbsp;</th><th>Filename</th><th>Size</th><th>Description</th><th>Date</th><th>&nbsp;</th></tr><tr bgcolor="#dddccc"><td><form class="fr" method="post" action="/file.php"><input type="image" src="/img/dl.gif" alt="Download"/><input type="hidden" name="file" value="bWFnL2NyaXMxLnppcA@@"/></form></td><td><a name="f159"></a><small><a href="/dl/mag/cris1.zip">cris1.zip</a></small></td><td><small>109658</small></td><td><small>[1]</small></td><td><small>Nov 1993</small></td><td><ul class="contents">
<li>001. <a href="#intro">How Did Cris Start: Where Is It Going? The story from the beginning</a></li>
<li>002. C.R.I.S. BBS Policies and Procedures</li>
<li>003. The Beginners Guide To Virus Research (Part One: EXE & COM Infecters)</li>
<li>004. How You Can Add Your Own Virus Signatures To your Scanner</li>
